  m_text: 'Bees are an essential part of our ecosystems.

    The mission doesn''t
    end here. Whether you have a garden or a balcony, planting native flowers helps
    protect your local ecosystem.


    And shoutout to the Guerrilla Gardeners out
    there helping to make our world a better place.'
